sub_title: Founder & CEO @ Sirius | Techstars’23 | Building Tech Stack for Sustainability Officers of Tomorrow
summary:
Sustainability junkie and passionate women & diversity advocate, on a mission to empower every business to drive impact.

Built from the ground up and led sustainability function in a $10b mining company. After starting a corporate startup Re|Source, delivering supply chain traceability for companies like Tesla and Glencore, I co-founded Sirius. Sirius solves structural and equity problems with sustainability transformation, that I know first hand after working in the mining sector for 9+ years. We are making decarbonization simple and accessible to every business.

Member of Net Zero steering committee of the World Economic Forum and the deputy governor of the Mining and Metals platform.
